{
  "stem": "26276.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of people tried to escape from work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we were working outside, especially building, at that time I remember I was throwing bricks all day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the guys, the builders, that were on top on the first or second floor, I had to-- they made us like-- out of a board, with two sticks hanging over the shoulders, so it should be able to rest on your shoulders.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a little shelf on the bottom in the back, they kept piling up bricks on it, right up to the top.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you had to climb up on this wooden ladder to deliver those bricks for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After that, they thought that was too slow, so they made us throw the bricks, you know, like from down the ground to the first floor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From the first floor, another one would catch it and throw it to the second and third floor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And our hands became so bad, that it looked like raw meat is hanging down from the bricks thrown.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had no gloves or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the roughness of the stone would just eat into the fingers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did it like this in most all the camps, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was I think in '43.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After we finished that, they shipped us to another camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to do the same thing all over again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the prison camps, everybody was all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, nobody would be better than the-- than the next, except the kapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what a kapo is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, he was the one who had all the say, to line us up, to be responsible for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He would hit us even sometimes during the day if you didn't do the work right or fast enough.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
